Your band's backdrop is prime real estate in your reception tent—and we say don't waste an inch! Set the scene for a vibrant dance floor and epic night, just like we did with help from @blossoms_events at Lacey & Bryan's Charleston wedding.

It truly took a village to bring this one to life. Taking cues from our bride’s innate style, we ran wild with our creative license and had a few fave Southern blooms hand-drawn in indigo and scaled up. So many artists + hours behind this gorge shot!
